text.tspan: WARNING: d is updated with T1 ONLY.
T2 is added ONLY to a.

ol.li: a, b, c shift down to b, c, d
e, f, g shift down to f, g, h
e is the 'mid-point' injection: new_e = old_d + T1
a is the 'head' injection: new_a = T1 + T2

div.p: c uint32_t T1 = h + Sigma1(e) + Ch(e, f, g) + K[t] + W[t];
